item.description: Once in the evening, Iâ€™ve been helping Google to save Bunny Planet. My friend from India told me that forest pythons are extremely dangerous. He said: Nick, you a good man, but your bear fighting skills that you developed during childhood in Russia will barely help you if you will meet such a big snake as a python in a forest. So, I was looking for some docs about interaction with pythons: tips from masters, evidence of survivals.
